reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Firmer than most - a plus!
reviews.reviewText: My old cushion has seen better days and when I saw this one I knew I had to order it. It's very comfortable and a bit larger than the one I had. It provides comfort for me sitting long hours. It actually comes with two covers! Now I can wash one while a clean one is put on. I've never seen any that come with two covers so it's a pleasant surprise!I'm a plus size so any cushion I use has to put up with a great deal. This one seems to do it better than others I've tried. The silicone is durable and washes up easily. The cover is smooth on one side and has gripper buds on the other side to keep it in place. It's a generous size - 16.9 x 14.5 inches and about 1.5 inches high.I'm enjoying the cushion and may have to get another one to replace the one I have in the car. I believe most anyone will find this to be a great bargain and a big comfort.
